# project driver that loads and resolves the module graph
#
# Parses mach.toml (plus every dep's own mach.toml), selects the active target,
# DFS-walks the module graph starting from the target's entrypoint, and runs
# resolve over every reachable module in topological order. The DFS post-order
# is the topological order, so no separate sort runs. During the load walk,
# `$if` predicates are evaluated against an incrementally-built ComptimeCtx -
# target params plus already-loaded imports' pub comptime constants plus this
# module's earlier pub comptime vals - so each module sees the same constant
# environment when it later runs through resolve. The public entry is
# build_project, which returns a fully populated Project or an error string.

